lead_paragraph: The image of sprightly gymnasts tumbling across a balance beam has always drawn American viewers during the Olympics, just like pictures of bikini-clad beach volleyball players going for gold.

headline.print_headline: American Women Trump Men in Medal Pursuit at Rio Olympics
